-- ⊢∘ DEBATE — ITERATION 2
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- Target: argue-for (∴ block = iteration 1 version, addresses false-trust)
-- Target: argue-against (∴ block refined to address audit-trail insufficiency)
